32641222512551220839.Text: You may pray at Imperial cult healing altars and receive blessings which cure common and blight diseases, cure poisons, and restore attributes. Non-members pay 25 drakes. Newer members pay 10 drakes, while higher-ranking members receive blessings free. Healing altars are found in: Vivec Foreign Quarter; Wolverine Hall in Sadrith Mora; Fort Buckmoth; Fort Moonmoth; Fort Pelagiad; Fort Darius; Ald'ruhn Guild of Mages, and Imperial Chapels in Ebonheart.
